title: Phish - Stanford University 1992/04/18  [SBD]  (FLAC)
description:
This is a copy of the ph1992-04-18.4524.shnf from bt.etree.org.

I have simply named the tracks and all that stuff.

It says ".shn" but I converted it to FLAC.

An excellent, classic Phish show.

I'll have you know that the shows from April 1992, specifically from 4/15 to 4/25, but even MORE specifically from 4/15/92 - 4/18/92, these are simply some of the best shows in the Phish catalog.  4/16/92 (Anaconda Theatre - Santa Barbara, CA) is probably the heaviest bootleg/circulated Phish show there is, perhaps maybe 7/25/92 and a few others.  It was released on "commercial" CD bootleg "Follow Me To Gamehendge" which apparently everyone in the universe had a cassette copy of in the mid-1990's.
